      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled CFD solver with documented release notes and basic regression testing sufficient for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional license with version control records. Release notes and known-issue documentation reviewed. Regression test suite confirms solver stability for rotating machinery applications. Meets Gradation 1 requirements for MRL 2."
