      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstration that the solver correctly implements the governing equations for incompressible turbulent flow through published benchmark cases.",
      "rationale": "Solver verified against FDA nozzle benchmark (FDA critical path) and lid-driven cavity problem. Published verification results for ANSYS Fluent on these cases confirm correct implementation of RANS equations. Meets Gradation 1."
