      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported for primary QoI (volume-averaged shear stress and RHI) using at least three mesh refinement levels; GCI < 5% on fine mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed: coarse (2.1M cells), medium (5.8M cells), fine (14.2M cells). Richardson extrapolation applied; GCI on fine mesh = 3.2% for RHI and 2.8% for volume-averaged shear stress. Discretization error within acceptance threshold. Meets Gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
