      "rationale": "In vitro experiments conducted per ASTM F1841 protocol. Flow rates (2, 3, 4, 5, 6 L/min) and rotational speeds (2000, 2500, 3000, 3500, 4000 RPM) documented in test report TR-2023-CPB-001. Fluid properties (37°C bovine blood analog, viscosity 3.5 cP) match CFD boundary conditions. Meets Gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
