      "rationale": "CFD predictions compared against experimental RHI measurements at all 5 flow-speed combinations. Mean absolute percentage error = 8.3% across operating points. CFD correctly ranks worst-case operating condition (5 L/min, 4000 RPM) in 4 of 5 experimental replicates. Meets Gradation 2 output comparison requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
