      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry identical to the COU device. Operating conditions cover the full 5-point flow-speed matrix specified in the COU. Blood analog fluid properties match clinical CPB conditions. Validation domain directly overlaps COU domain. Meets Gradation 2."
